name: SVGTests
description: The SVGTests interface is used to reflect conditional processing attributes and is mixed into other interfaces for elements that support these attributes.

members.name: SVGTests.requiredFeatures
members.description: An SVGStringList corresponding to the requiredFeatures attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGTests.requiredExtensions
members.description: An SVGStringList corresponding to the requiredExtensions attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGTests.systemLanguage
members.description: An SVGStringList corresponding to the systemLanguage attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGTests.hasExtension()
members.description: Returns true if the browser supports the given extension, specified by a URI.
